data.description: Lots of room in this 4 Bedroom, 2+ Bath home situated on a corner lot.  You will be amazed at the Second Floor Bath/Dressing room with Jacuzzi Tub and Separate High End Shower as well as walk-in closet.  There is a Main Floor Bath and Utility as well as a Main floor Bedroom along with Family, Living, Dining and Large Eat-in Kitchen.  Newer Furnace and Central Air and oversized Two Car Attached Garage.  Welcome to Great Living in Fantastic Community of Walnut.
